SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4579
A bill to amend 1979 PA 94, entitled
"The state school aid act of 1979,"
by amending sections 201, 204, 206, 207a, 207b, 207c, 210, 210b,
210d, 212, 217, 217a, 217b, 222, 229a, and 230 (MCL 388.1801,
388.1804, 388.1806, 388.1807a, 388.1807b, 388.1807c, 388.1810,
388.1810b, 388.1810d, 388.1812, 388.1817, 388.1817a, 388.1817b,
388.1822, 388.1829a, and 388.1830), sections 201, 206, 207a, 207b,
207c, 217, 217b, 222, 229a, and 230 as amended by 2024 PA 120,
section 204 as amended by 2012 PA 201, section 210 as amended and
section 210d as added by 2015 PA 85, section 210b as amended by
2021 PA 86, section 212 as amended by 2016 PA 249, and section 217a
as added by 2023 PA 103, and by adding sections 217d, 217e, 217f,
217g, 217h, and 217i; and to repeal acts and parts of acts.
